    {
      "note_no": "2937",
      "note": "The verb for \"send me back\" is in the plural in Arabic, which is construed either (1) as an emphatic form, as if the singular were repeated, or (2) as a plural of respect, though such a plural is not ordinarily used in addressing Allah, or (3) as a plural addressed to the angels, after the address to Allah in \"O my Lord!\""
